sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Your Application
    participant Orch as IOrchestrationService
    participant Ctx as Session Context
    participant LLM as LLM Provider
    participant Tools as Agent Tools
    participant Obs as Observer

    App->>Orch: OrchestrateAsync(sessionId, message, policy)
    activate Orch

    Orch->>Ctx: GetOrCreateContext(sessionId)
    Ctx-->>Orch: SessionContext (conversation history)

    Orch->>Obs: OnOrchestrationStarting

    Note over Orch: Orchestration Loop Begins

    Note over Orch,Tools: Iteration 1

    Orch->>Obs: OnBeforeLlmCall
    Orch->>LLM: SendAsync(messages + tools)
    LLM-->>Orch: Response (tool_call: get_forecast)
    Orch->>Obs: OnResponseGenerated

    Orch->>Obs: OnToolCallRequested(get_forecast)
    Obs-->>Orch: Approved
    Orch->>Tools: Invoke get_forecast(city: "Seattle")
    Tools-->>Orch: { temp: 62, conditions: "partly cloudy" }
    Orch->>Obs: OnToolExecuted(get_forecast, 45ms)

    Orch->>Ctx: Append tool call + result to history

    Note over Orch,Tools: Iteration 2

    Orch->>Obs: OnBeforeLlmCall
    Orch->>LLM: SendAsync(messages + tool result)
    LLM-->>Orch: Response (text: "The forecast for Seattle is 62°...")
    Orch->>Obs: OnResponseGenerated

    Note over Orch: No tool calls — loop complete

    Orch->>Ctx: Append final response to history

    Orch->>Ctx: Persist context (ContextChanged)
    Orch->>Obs: OnOrchestrationComplete

    Orch-->>App: OrchestratorResult
    deactivate Orch

    Note over App: result.FinalMessage = "The forecast for Seattle is 62°..."
    Note over App: result.TotalIterations = 2
    Note over App: result.TotalToolCalls = 1
